OL,5, A climber killed in an avalanche on Ben
OL,6, Nevis has been named as Mark Bessell, a
OL,7, 48-year-old teacher from Bristol.      
OL,9,FMr Bessell died climbing the north face
OL,10,Fof the mountain 30 December, while a   
OL,11,Fsecond man suffered serious injuries.  
OL,13,FRichard Uffendell, headteacher of      
OL,14,FAshton Park School, paid tribute to Mr 
OL,15,FBessell as a "well-respected and       
OL,16,Flong-standing member of our staff".    
OL,18,FIn a letter to parents, he said Mr     
OL,19,FBessell had "such a positive impact" on
OL,20,Fthe lives of many students.            
